---
title: block_construction (osaka-blocks)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_set_header : header = Header
    q_set_header --> q_set_transactions : transactions = Tuple[Bytes | LegacyTransaction, ...]
    q_set_transactions --> q_set_ommers : ommers = Tuple[Header, ...]
    q_set_ommers --> q_set_withdrawals : withdrawals = Tuple[Withdrawal, ...]
    q_set_withdrawals --> q_final : freeze(Block)
    q_final --> [*] : done

    note right of q_set_ommers
        INV: Block is slotted_freezable (immutable after construction).
        ommers tuple is always empty in PoS forks.
    end note

    note right of q_set_transactions
        INV: transactions may contain any supported transaction type
        (Legacy, AccessList, FeeMarket, Blob, SetCode)
    end note
